#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This time, simply leave a note about the why this is booked and save the "
"slot."
msgstr ""
"Esta vez solo deja una nota que explique el motivo de la reservación y "
"guarda el horario."

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Those city tax are now due as well as any other additional services consumed "
"during the\n"
"            stay."
msgstr ""
"Estos impuestos locales deberán ser pagados, así como cualquier otro "
"servicio adicional consumido durante la\n"
"            estadía."

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.guest_house_order_search
msgid "To Check In"
msgstr "Para el registro de entrada"

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.guest_house_order_search
